All Classes

Class Description
AutoNumbersEntry
A child class of Entry class where automated entries are generated
Bill
Class that stores individual bills information, can be updated in the list in DataProvider
Competition
Abstract class that stores a competition's information including entries, parent class of child classes LuckyNumbersCompetition and RandomPickCompetition
DataAccessException
Exception class that gets thrown when there is error in data access
DataFormatException
Exception class that gets thrown when there is error in data format
DataProvider
Class in charge of unloading the input files into arraylist of data to be used throughout the program, class also in charge of outputting into a new csv file via updateFile method
Entry
Class that stores information regarding any entries, parent class of NumbersEntry and AutoNumbersEntry
LuckyNumbersCompetition
Child Class of Competition class, created when competition this mode is selected
Member
Class that stores individual members information, can be updated in the list in DataProvider
NumbersEntry
A child class of Entry class where manual entries are inputted through methods of this class
RandomPickCompetition
Child Class of Competition class, created when competition this mode is selected
SimpleCompetitions
Class that stores all competitions' information
